Some 3D pixel art with our beloved and emblematic Chuck.

![3D pixel Chuck](http://i.imgur.com/N0bZBDf.png)

Hand made with love, pixel bloc by pixel bloc, on the awesome [voxelbuilder](http://voxelbuilder.com/#:C/2ecc713498db34495ee67e22ecf0f1000000) and exported in STL model thanks to the node.js lib [ndarray-stl](https://github.com/maxogden/ndarray-stl).

We know need to put our hand on a 3D printer to have a cute ninja!
